HEADWORD: Nebbish
<hw>Neb"bish</hw> <pr>(m⟦ecr⟧b"⟦icr⟧sh)</pr> <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Yiddish, <ets>nebekh</ets> poor, unfortunate.]</ety> <def>A person
